text.section:
There is hereby established a "Teachers' National Certification Incentive Trust Fund" in the State Treasury for the purposes of:
Funding stipends for teachers to prepare for certification by the National Board for Professional Teaching Standards;
Reimbursing a portion of the certification fee to each teacher who is awarded national board certification;
Reimbursing local boards of education or the Department of Education for persons who serve as substitute teachers for national board certification candidates; and
Funding stipends for national board certified teachers who serve as mentors to other teachers within the school district or the Kentucky Tech system.
